{"tid":2402984,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城今季等奪冠？","createTime":"2021-02-10T22:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T16:29:21.000Z","uid":7516,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"818ce3a3d7e13736270c643d3347795db407c585","tid":2402984,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:12:51.000Z","msg":"餘下英超 有實力既對手得返<br />\n<br />\n熱刺<br />\n曼聯<br />\n李斯特城<br />\n<br />\n以上3隊「好彩」既話，其中一隊贏到曼城<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車路士 和都偷笑<br />\n阿仙奴 垃圾出奇蹟<br />\n狼隊 死守反擊<br />\n愛華頓 <br />\n<br />\n依加打少場，已經領先曼狗5分，估計個場都執埋啫係領先8分，基本上除左曼狗數字上有機會贏，其他都已經要保4/衝4<br />\n<br />\n估唔到曼城開季柒下柒下，2月就榜首，第十輪個陣仲係排14<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XGmbOF4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGmbOF4.png&h=8174c7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得返1.04係咪可以allin等收息，買1萬賺400好過放銀行買滙豐<br />\n<br />\n利申：買左熱刺、愛華頓冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c71f8aa2c7cc445fcc85d902e1f880bb0a2ac7e","tid":2402984,"uid":163959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:35:11.000Z","msg":"聽日買拜仁世冠杯冠軍 都有4%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收完錢再買Psg拎法甲 仲有25%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20809e57bb7c70b3f4ff2e5e8d48f6ae08f17431","tid":2402984,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T22:51:41.000Z","msg":"熱狗殘哂先打鏝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c457eb9b6cc3a62f47a8f4615b05932ff848b66","tid":2402984,"uid":84081,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T23:20:18.000Z","msg":"上半季贏咗車路士，畀林伯起機之後<br />\n曼城奪冠個賠率得返唔夠2倍<br />\n個陣開呢個post都話<br />\n<br />\n依家1.04先開post有咩用<img src=\"/assets/fa